Darija_Arabe: "قال ""خليونا نحتفلو"" وخودوني للبار. وقال بلي كان غادي يدير مكالمة هاتفية وغومشا ومرجعش وخلاني واحل بفاتورة كبيرة."
Arabizi: "qal 'khliwna n7tflo' wkhodoni lbar. wqal bli kan ghadi ydir mokalama hatifiya wghomsha wmarja3ch wkhallani wa7el bfatora kbira."
Anglais: "He said, 'Let’s celebrate,' and took me to the bar. He said he was going to make a phone call, disappeared, and didn’t come back, leaving me stuck with a big bill."
